comments: She is a really easy prof to take. She makes her power point entertaining and is always happy. The notebook are easy to do and she gives u the right answer afterwards. Her test are basically off the notebook and her study guide is helpful. A really nice person as well. Also HOT
Easiest class I have ever taken. Just show up. she goes over the chapter before you do the lab in your group in class. She gives you a study guide for the quizzes which are multiple choice. Easy A.
Simple daily assignments out of the workbook and 3 short quizzes. Hot professor.

Wow! HOT! If her boyfriend didn\'t make Leonidas look like a midget, I\'d totally have asked her out after the semester was over! Oh well.. She is really helpful, super enthusiastic and really knows her stuff! Someone said her bf won all the departments scholarships or something, so I guess I better start studying and join the campus gym then retake!

WOW!She is by far the most gorgous teacher I have encounterd. She is willing to help any student in need. The subject was very intersting and all you have to do is show up and do the labs and you will pass. There are three exams(quizes)and they consisted of twenty questions each. The study guide she provides gives you all the info on the exams.EASY

Geography isn?t my subject but I really enjoyed the way Professor Stern explained things. She really tried to make everything relevant to us. I don?t think I?ll ever use map projections again but at least I know how to.
Ms. Stern was understanding and extremely helpful. She took the time to help me as much as I needed.
She is really cool and makes me want to do well.
She is cool, but she keeps us to the minute and once she starts talking, she goes on tangents for days. Otherwise, shes alright.
Interesting labs; knows what she is talking about.
